OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry today with plenty of
OL,6,Fsunshine. A veil of high cloud will
OL,7,Fmove across for a time, making the
OL,8,Fsunshine hazy, but it will still feel
OL,9,Fwarm in the light winds, and clearer
OL,10,Fweather will develop during the
OL,11,Fafternoon.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FStaying dry tonight with
OL,14,Fclear skies for a while, though some
OL,15,Fcloud arriving from the east.
OL,16,FTemperatures will fall under the clear
OL,17,Fspells to give a patchy rural frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
