OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FAfter a chilly start, it will
OL,6,Fbe another warm day with light winds.
OL,7,FSome bright or sunny spells, but
OL,8,Fcloudier than on Saturday. A small
OL,9,Fchance of a shower later.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,12,FStaying largely dry at the start of
OL,13,Fnext week. Skies will be cloudier at
OL,14,Ftimes, but there will still be some
OL,15,Fwarm sunny spells. Becoming breezy on
OL,16,FWednesday. Chilly nights.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
